An arrangement that parents make for their young children to play together.

76
00:05:23.000 --> 00:05:29.000
A small group of people who spend a lot of time together and may seem unfriendly towards other people.

77
00:05:29.000 --> 00:05:34.000
Glam is short for glamorous, meaning visually attractive and exciting.

78
00:05:34.000 --> 00:05:40.000
If you fit into a group of people, you belong and feel accepted by them because you're similar to them.

79
